y identified on mammography: correlation with imaging outcome and pathologic findings. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2007;188(3):667–675.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.06.0413">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17312052/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Developing+asymmetry+identified+on+mammography%3A+correlation+with+imaging+outcome+and+pathologic+findings&amp;author=JWT+Leung&amp;author=EA+Sickles&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=667-675&amp;doi=10.2214%2FAJR.06.0413&amp;pmid=17312052">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Shetty MK, Watson AB. Sonographic evaluation of focal asymmetric density of the breast. <em>Ultrasound Q</em> 2002;18(2):115–121.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/00013644-200206000-00004">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12970607/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Sonographic+evaluation+of+focal+asymmetric+density+of+the+breast&amp;author=MK+Shetty&amp;author=AB+Watson&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;journal=Ultrasound+Q&amp;pages=115-121&amp;doi=10.1097%2F00013644-200206000-00004&amp;pmid=12970607">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Wang LC, Sullivan M, Du H, Feldman MI, Mendelson EB. US appearance of ductal carcinoma in situ. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2013;33(1):213–228.</div><div class="external-